A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Environment – Building Energy Performance Standards – Agricultural
3 Buildings
4 FOR the purpose of prohibiting the Department of the Environment from requiring an
5 owner, lessor, lessee, or operator of an agricultural building to apply to the
6 Department for an exemption from certain building energy performance standards;
7 and generally relating to building energy performance standards and agricultural
8 buildings.
